<li id="cite_note-Alberts-22">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Alberts_22-0" title=""><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Alberts_22-1" title=""><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFBruce_AlbertsAlexander_JohnsonJulian_LewisMartin_Raff2009"><a href="/wiki/Bruce_Alberts" title="Bruce Alberts">Bruce Alberts</a>; Alexander Johnson; Julian Lewis; Martin Raff; Keith Roberts; <a href="/wiki/Peter_Walter" title="Peter Walter">Peter Walter</a> (March, 2002), <i>Molecular Biology of the Cell</i> (4th ed.), Routledge, <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0815332181" class="internal">ISBN 0-8153-3218-1</a></cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Molecular+Biology+of+the+Cell&amp;rft.aulast=Bruce+Alberts&amp;rft.au=Bruce+Alberts&amp;rft.au=Alexander+Johnson&amp;rft.au=Julian+Lewis&amp;rft.au=Martin+Raff&amp;rft.au=Keith+Roberts&amp;rft.au=Peter+Walter&amp;rft.date=March%2C+2002&amp;rft.edition=4th&amp;rft.pub=Routledge&amp;rft.isbn=0-8153-3218-1&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Evolution_as_theory_and_fact"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-Shubin-23"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Shubin_23-0" title="">^</a></b> "<cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFShubin.2C_Neil.2008">Shubin, Neil. (2008). <i>Your Inner Fish</i>. Pantheon. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/9780375424472" class="internal">ISBN 9780375424472</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Your+Inner+Fish&amp;rft.aulast=Shubin%2C+Neil.&amp;rft.au=Shubin%2C+Neil.&amp;rft.date=2008&amp;rft.pub=Pantheon&amp;rft.isbn=9780375424472&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Evolution_as_theory_and_fact"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
</ol>
</div>
